BOOK EVENT
EVENTS MENU
EVENTS TO-GO MENU
Gatherings, Italian Style
Perfect for any celebration with family and friends or colleagues. We offer a wide array of intimate spaces for your gathering including showers, rehearsal dinners, wedding receptions, cocktail party, and birthday celebrations with extended family and loved ones.
The Familia Room up to 25 Guests
Our Famila Room is a perfect setting for a rehearsal dinner, anniversary party, shower, or any corporate meeting event.
Terrazza up to 25 Guests
Our Terraza is a perfect gathering space for lunch and dinner meetings, networking socials, anniversaries, birthdays, or any celebration.
The Piccola Room up to 14 Guests
Our Piccola Room is the perfect intimate setting for business meetings, birthday dinners or any special occasion.
Patio
Our Patio is the perfect outdoor setting for a happy hour, cocktail party, or any social gathering occasion.
*These rooms are available separately or combined to create the most unique private event.
